'''諾頓'''（{{lang|en|'''Norton'''}}）為[[美國|美國]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[諾頓縣_(堪薩斯州)|諾頓縣]]的一座城市，也是諾頓縣的[[县城|縣治]]所在地<ref name="GR6">{{cite web|url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|accessdate=2011-06-07|title=Find a County|publisher=National Association of Counties|archive-date=2012-07-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6962cjXgL?url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此城市人口有2,928人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web |title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau |accessdate=2011-03-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721034521/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table |archivedate=2011-07-21 }}</ref>。

==歷史==
諾頓於1872年設立<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA253#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Biennial Report of the Board of Directors of the Kansas State Historical Society | publisher=Kansas State Printing Plant | author=Kansas State Historical Society | year=1916 | pages=253 | access-date=2016-07-08 | archive-date=2017-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171106234513/https://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA253#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。城市名與所屬縣份一樣皆以聯邦上尉奧爾洛夫·諾頓（Orloff Norton）來命名<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=4895 | title=Profile for Norton, Kansas | publisher=[[ePodunk|ePodunk]] | accessdate=2014-06-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715004912/http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=4895 | archive-date=2014-07-15 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

首幢以{{le|原木屋|log house|原木}}築成的飯店於1873年建成<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Qi9cXyTWt9EC&pg=PA374#v=onepage&q&f=true | title=Kansas: A Cyclopedia of State History, Volume 2 | publisher=Standard Publishing Company | author=Blackmar, Frank Wilson | year=1912 | pages=374 | access-date=2016-07-08 | archive-date=2014-10-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030205229/http://books.google.com/books?id=Qi9cXyTWt9EC&pg=PA374#v=onepage&q&f=true | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==地理==
諾頓坐落在北緯39度50分0秒、西經99度53分27秒（亦可表示為39.833338, -99.890899）處<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060720110047/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2006-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積為{{convert|1.93|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，全境皆為陸地<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此城市坐落於諾頓縣境內的{{le|普雷里多格溪|Prairie Dog Creek}}北邊。在美國農墾局於1963年建造{{le|基思西貝利厄斯湖|Keith Sebelius Lake}}之前，諾頓經常飽受水患，因此在此城市西南方{{convert|2.5|mi}}處興建大壩方得解決水患問題<ref>{{cite web| title= Project Details - Almena Unit| publisher= [[United_States_Bureau_of_Reclamation|United States Bureau of Reclamation]]| url= http://www.usbr.gov/projects/Project.jsp?proj_Name=Almena+Unit| accessdate= 2010-11-02| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150905053016/http://www.usbr.gov/projects/Project.jsp?proj_Name=Almena+Unit| archive-date= 2015-09-05| dead-url= yes}}</ref>。內布拉斯加州州界位於此城市北方{{convert|11|mi}}處。

===氣候===
諾頓坐落於[[副热带湿润气候|副热带湿润气候]]和[[半乾旱氣候|半乾旱氣候]]兩氣候區的邊界上。此地區1月平均低溫15°F（-9.4°C），7月平均高溫94°F（34.4°C），年溫差較大。此地區全年平均降水量有{{convert|21.1|in}}，降水量相對較低，而全年平均降雪量達{{convert|25.1|in}}。

